<p><a name="Gauss_windows" id="Gauss_windows"></a></p>
<h4><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Window_function&amp;action=edit&amp;section=16" title="Edit section: Gauss windows">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Gauss windows</span></h4>
<dl>
<dd><img class="tex" alt="w(n)=e^{-\frac{1}{2} \left ( \frac{n-(N-1)/2}{\sigma (N-1)/2} \right)^{2}}" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/math/a/d/a/ada213aaebbd218ca1cb091fde5c4378.png" /></dd>
