<h4><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Window_function&amp;action=edit&amp;section=17" title="Edit section: Bartlett–Hann window">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Bartlett–Hann window</span></h4>
<dl>
<dd><img class="tex" alt="w(n)=a_0 - a_1 \left |\frac{n}{N-1}-\frac{1}{2} \right| - a_2 \cos \left (\frac{2 \pi n}{N-1}\right )" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/math/8/b/e/8be54957f4b95f17b77a713c34549a8c.png" /></dd>
</dl>
<dl>
<dd><img class="tex" alt="a_0=0.62;\quad a_1=0.48;\quad a_2=0.38\," src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/math/2/6/0/26010d923306233913db3ba3132cbbf8.png" /></dd>
</dl>
<div style="clear:both"></div>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:182px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Window_function_(blackman).png" class="image" title="Blackman window; α = 0.16; B=1.73"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/cb/Window_function_%28blackman%29.png/180px-Window_function_%28blackman%29.png" width="180" height="73" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
